data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this delightful single-story home, nestled in the serene Red River Ranch subdivision of Cibolo, Texas. This move-in-ready residence spans 1,438 square feet and sits on a spacious 0.15-acre lot, making it an ideal choice for families or as a sound investment opportunity.    Property Features:  - Home Specs: 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, 1,438 sq ft, 0.15 Acres Lot  - Kitchen & Dining: Open layout with granite countertops, Whirlpool Stainless Steel appliances, and a large dining area  - Master Suite: Includes a roomy ensuite with a spacious walk-in closet  - Interior Upgrades: 9-foot ceilings, 2-inch faux wood blinds throughout, and pre-plumbing for a water softener loop  - Outdoor Space: Large, fenced backyard perfect for private family activities or entertaining    Convenient Location:  - Proximity to Education and Recreation: Close to local schools and easy access to The Forum, Retama Park, and Randolph Air Force Base    - Accessibility: Only 5 minutes from downtown Cibolo, with quick drives to shopping, dining, and downtown attractions    Investment Opportunity: This property represents a unique opportunity, thanks to its desirable features and prime location. It offers potential for both personal enjoyment and investment returns, given its readiness for immediate occupancy and well-maintained condition.    Don't Miss Out: Schedule your visit today to see why 529 Cypress Bayou should be your next home or investment. With its charming features and excellent location, this property is poised to be a delightful home for its new owners. Don't wait-explore how this home can meet your needs and exceed your expectations!
